= Use code blocks in lists

To include a code block in a list use `+` to indicate the code block belongs to the list item:

[source,asc]
-----
. List item 1
+
[source,sh]
----
echo "Hello World"
----
. List item 2
-----

Which will be rendered like this:

'''

. List item 1
+
[source,sh]
----
echo "Hello World"
----
. List item 2


'''
